---
// Pass-through of Starlight's default Head.
//
// NOTE: We previously added Astro's <ClientRouter /> here for SPA-style
// no-flash navigation. It broke Pagefind search: Starlight initialises the
// search UI on first load, but a view-transition swap inserts a fresh, empty
// search dialog without re-running that init, so search came up blank on every
// soft-navigated page. Full-page navigation re-initialises search each time,
// so we keep the default behaviour. If SPA nav is wanted back, it must come
// with a Search component override that uses `transition:persist` (or an
// `astro:page-load` re-init) so the search UI survives the swap.
import Default from "@astrojs/starlight/components/Head.astro";
---

<Default><slot /></Default>
